much, and we never got the chance to even test that out. But the way Anastasia said it, implies that I am the one at fault for causing all the arguments. This is completely
unfair to me, and I feel that both me and Jia Yi had a role to play. And not once did I give up on wanting to work things out with Jia Yi. I truly believe, and I feel
