Anastasia said that Jia Yi is the most fragile and emotional person. One of the root causes of all my arguments with Jia Yi is her inability to show emotion at times,
and her emotional unavailability. Jia Yi also isn't fragile. Jia Yi is strong, and has been through so much. How on earth can her best friend discredit her by calling her
fragile?

Lastly, before Anastasia blocked me, she said "As much as I like to help people, this is getting out of hand". Excuse me? Help people? Before the overdose, I called her
