/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////// Thoughts - 08/04/22 ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

The night of the overdose, I have been feeling very anxious, as Jia Yi has not talked to me for 5 days, wanted to break up, then didn't reply when I wanted
to have a conversation about it. I messaged her in the morning, then at midnight again, asking to talk. She didn't reply, which made my anxiety worse. I started getting
