My actions also hurt Jia Yi. I am not denying that fact, and that is my biggest regret. If I died that night, but it didn't hurt Jia Yi, I would have been fine with it.
But I did hurt Jia Yi, and I am regretful.

But I did reflect. And at first, after IMH, I told myself that I jumped to conclusions, that I pretended that Jia Yi ignored me causing me to spiral. It was all in my 
head. But last night, I checked the logs. The first two calls that went through took place at 1.06, and 1.07 am. The third call, which I assumed was after she turned
