So there it was. The main catalyst that made me spiral to the point of overdosing, was my assumption that Jia Yi ignored me. A major source of guilt for me, was that
I wrongfully assumed Jia Yi ignored me, which caused all the pain to happen. I was cruel and unthoughtful, all because I jumped to conclusions. I unthoughtfully
jumped to conclusions

